Game Lists: Gear, Spells, & More
This section serves as a reference for the common equipment and abilities you will encounter in Skyrim. Use it to understand the gear in your starting kit and the treasures you might find on your adventures.

Armor & Clothing List
Armor is more than just protection; it defines your character's style and strategy. Each set provides Damage Reduction (DR) but also comes with unique properties. Choosing your armor is a trade-off between resilience, mobility, and other powerful benefits. This list covers the common types found in Skyrim; unique, enchanted, or legendary variants may exist at your GM's discretion.
